						”Touching Images. Please Touch”,
						<i>View. Theories and Practices of Visual Culture</i>
						 12 (2015), 
						<a href="https://doi.org/10.36854/widok/2015.12.915" target="_blank">https://doi.org/10.36854/widok/2015.12.915</a>
